                                This project is for brushing up my jdbc skills.
 
 
 General steps for JDBC operations
 
Step 1: Load the JDBC driver.

Step 2: Create Connection object.

Step 3: Create objects of (Query, Statement, PreparedStatemenst, CallableStatement)
Note:(You will not have to create objects for all of this. Depending on requirement you will have to create. 
Refer the code for exact operations of this classes/interfaces). 
 
 
Step 4: Process the data.

Step 5: Close the Connection object.


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


In this demonstration we will fire query using statement object.